<span id="freeTextContainer16607814121755304214">This was my second read from the &quot;Anna Curtis&quot; series. Both were enjoyable, fast paced and well-written. Leotta educates while she thrills. I learned a lot about the MS-13 gang that I didn&apos;t know before. If you like crime stories but also like humanity and want to learn something, this series is perfect.</span>
  <span id="freeText16607814121755304214" style="display:none">This was my second read from the "Anna Curtis" series. Both were enjoyable, fast paced and well-written. Leotta educates while she thrills. I learned a lot about the MS-13 gang that I didn't know before. If you like crime stories but also like humanity and want to learn something, this series is perfect.</span>
