  <span id="freeText17746967365794590441" style="display:none">Prosecutor Anna Curtis is chasing the devil ... but when you do that the devil might come for you!<br />While she is intensely working with her detectives to bring down the infamous MS13 gang in Washington DC, Anna is also preparing and enjoying her future wedding with Homicide Chief Jack Bailey and focusing on her relationship with Olivia, her future step daughter. The deeper she digs in the case, the more dangerous and treacherous her professional and private life becomes. Can she trust her own detectives and can she be sure that her future husband loves her for the 100 %.<br />Great mystery full of twists and turns. Hard to put down.</span>
